    "course_title": "DRUG HISTORY: DANGEROUS DRUGS AND MAGIC BULLETS",
    "description": "A history of medicinal substances and dangerous drugs in wider context, with a focus on gender, race, class, business, and other analytical categories. \"Medicines\" and \"drugs\" change over time -- and concepts of risk, danger, legality, and even scientific evidence are elastic. Histories of laws, regulations, and key historical actors, as well as specific drug biographies, will be provided.",
